287
00:20:23,800 --> 00:20:26,040
kto by mu pomohol....

288
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:27,440
Vaša psychológia,

289
00:20:27,810 --> 00:20:31,010
sa nedá použiť na vraha.

290
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:35,050
Keď sa z človeka stane vrah,

291
00:20:35,380 --> 00:20:37,210
nezaslúži si od ľudí

292
00:20:38,050 --> 00:20:39,920
