357
00:25:18,530 --> 00:25:20,460
Ten muž, Chae Do Jin...

358
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:25,570
Kde by som ho mohla stretnúť?

359
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:29,310
Môžete sa s ním stretnúť,

360
00:25:29,310 --> 00:25:31,040
